#ROOM
Vnum     13000
Name     &dDarkshire Town Square&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The gloomy town of Darkshire serves as the only real sanctuary in the
cursed forest of Duskwood. A large bonfire burns in the center of the
square, constantly fed by the Night Watch. Commander Ebonlocke and the
Mayor discuss the defense of the town here.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    13002
Desc      The Town Hall.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    13023
Desc      The dark road leading east toward Deadwind Pass.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    13001
Desc      The Scarlet Raven Tavern.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    13003
Desc      The western outskirts of town.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 13000 1 13000
  Reset E 1 13000 10 16
Reset M 0 13001 1 13000
Reset M 0 13002 2 13000
  Reset E 1 13001 10 17
#ENDROOM

