Vnum     13007
Name     &dThe Duskwood Crossroads&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     A major intersection heavily shrouded in fog. A rotting wooden signpost
points north to Elwynn Forest, west to Westfall, and east to Darkshire.
The path to the south leads to the massive Ravenhill Cemetery.
~
