Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The barn doors have been clawed to pieces. Bloodstains on the floor tell
a grim story of the farmers' final moments. More rabid wolves sleep in
the hay lofts.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    13016
Desc      The farmhouse yard.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 13009 2 13017
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     13018
Name     &dThe Weaver's Web&d~
Sector   forest~
Desc     The forest is choked with webs. Mummified bodies of deer, wolves, and
even human travelers hang suspended in the trees. The giant Black Widows
skitter silently across the silk threads.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    13014
Desc      The deep orchard.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    13015
Desc      The Weeping Cave.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 13013 2 13018
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     13019
Name     &dThe Gloomy Path&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     This rough dirt path connects the Crossroads to the western reaches of
Duskwood. Defias Smugglers operate out of the heavy brush here, moving
goods between Westfall and the southern coast.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    13007
Desc      The Duskwood Crossroads.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    13016
Desc      The Yorgen Farmstead.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    13020
